        {
            "title": "澳洲3月CPI大幅上揚但略低於預期;核心通膨持平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yx5m80ObJELUhpLnMokzRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPECA10T7_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 受中東戰爭導致的燃料和航運中斷影響,澳洲3月消費者物價指數通膨大幅上升,但數據略低於預期,核心通膨則保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局(ABS)週三公布的數據顯示,截至3月31日的CPI年增4.6%。該數據略低於預期的4.8%,但較前一季度的3.7%大幅上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月CPI較前一個月增長1.1%,其中運輸成本因燃料價格上漲成為最大推動因素。這與美國-以色列對伊朗戰爭導致的全球油價大幅上漲趨勢一致。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-60b783f0-f088-3039-b7ea-5c55e2eb3820-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以修正均值CPI代表的核心通膨在3月上升3.3%,與前一個月持平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局物價統計主管蘇-艾倫·盧克(Sue-Ellen Luke)在聲明中表示:\"3月的增幅是自2017年該系列數據開始以來最大的單月增幅,反映了中東衝突對燃料價格的影響。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">房價上漲也對3月通膨增長有所貢獻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週三的數據反映了伊朗戰爭對燃料價格和通膨的影響。但數據也顯示潛在通膨有所穩定,特別是在澳洲儲備銀行今年兩次加息之後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B23%E6%9C%88cpi%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%8F%9A%E4%BD%86%E7%95%A5%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3-025331314.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 11:07:16",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普準備對伊朗實施長期封鎖,《華爾街日報》報導",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7vsPtL1T0bhwOtrhhdrpEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_4_M_1440048337.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據《華爾街日報》週二報導,美國總統唐納德·川普已指示助手為對伊朗實施長期封鎖做準備,這標誌著華盛頓在權衡衝突下一步行動時,轉向持續施加經濟壓力的策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報導援引美國官員的消息稱,川普選擇加強遏制伊朗石油出口的力度,並限制往返其港口的航運,認為封鎖比恢復大規模軍事打擊或尋求快速外交退出的風險更低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉是在4月停火之後採取的,當時停火結束了一場大規模轟炸行動,但該地區的緊張局勢仍然高漲。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2d5a5b82-cec6-3ec7-902a-9f6f62bb8cb5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》表示,川普最近拒絕了伊朗提出的三步驟提案,該提案原本會提前重新開放荷姆茲海峽,同時推遲核談判,川普認為該提案不足以滿足美國對德黑蘭核計劃施加限制的要求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導補充稱,川普不願放棄一項關鍵要求,即伊朗承諾暫停鈾濃縮活動至少20年,並在此期限之後接受限制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱,雖然封鎖被視為對伊朗經濟施壓的手段,但它也引發了長期對峙的前景,官員警告稱,隨著外交陷入僵局,衝突可能進入「無協議、無戰爭」階段。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%B0%8D%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E-023947754.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 11:07:18",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價自三週高點回落;阿聯退出OPEC,荷莫茲海峽持續受阻",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GEYnScJLxcDie9IJ8LFEPg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB8604B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 油價週三自三週高點小幅回落,市場正在評估阿拉伯聯合大公國退出<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"OPEC產油國組織\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:OPEC產油國組織;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/OPEC產油國組織\">OPEC產油國組織</a>的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但美國與以色列對伊朗戰爭的不確定性持續存在,限制了油價跌幅,因為<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>仍處於關閉狀態,華盛頓與德黑蘭之間的和平協議似乎遙遙無期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:16(北京時間00:16),布蘭特原油期貨下跌0.6%至110.65美元/桶,而美國WTI原油期貨下跌0.9%至99.05美元/桶。兩種合約週二均飆升逾3%,接近三週高點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-57ff131c-56e2-3d0a-afc4-4e0456a80fad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯的退出將於週五正式生效,這對在伊朗戰爭持續干擾下的產油國組織來說是一個重大打擊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯表示,此舉是為了更加專注於其\"國家利益\"。但此舉使該國與鄰國沙特阿拉伯(OPEC的實際領導者)產生分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該國很可能會增加石油產量,因為它過去曾反對OPEC的生產配額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但由於通過荷莫茲海峽的航運仍被封鎖,任何產量增加都可能只會在該通道重新開放後才會實現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種情況似乎遙遙無期,因為荷莫茲海峽仍處於關閉狀態,而促成更多美伊談判的嘗試基本上都失敗了。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週早些時候的媒體報導顯示,伊朗提出了一項新提案,以重新開放荷莫茲海峽並結束戰爭。但華盛頓被認為反對這一提案,原因是在推遲伊朗核計劃談判方面存在分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國也基本上維持了對伊朗的海上封鎖,使兩國陷入僵局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷莫茲海峽自2月下旬關閉以來,擾亂了全球約20%的石油供應,引發了原油價格的持續飆升。該通道在短期內似乎不太可能重新開放。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%89%E9%80%B1%E9%AB%98%E9%BB%9E%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%80%80%E5%87%BAopec-%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB-013405934.html",
